cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY, cs.RO 

The paper presents a neural network model for modelling complex natural and cultural phenomena using systems of simple interactions between particles. This falls under the broad category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The model is applied to physical dynamical systems, which suggests a connection to robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of visual input, which could relate to computer vision (cs.CV).
